    "body": "I get the following error when I build xsdk.\r\n\r\n```\r\n==> Installing netlib-scalapack\r\n==> Searching for binary cache of netlib-scalapack\r\n==> Warning: No Spack mirrors are currently configured\r\n==> No binary for netlib-scalapack found: installing from source\r\n==> Error: [Errno 13] Permission denied: '/-'\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n```console\r\n$ git checkout balay/test\r\n$ spack install xsdk\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Information on your system\r\n\r\nThis error occurred on multiple machines [ubuntu-18.04, Mac OSX, other linuxes]\r\n\r\nSometimes the error goes away when I redo the build.\r\n\r\nNote: This is with latest develop + xsdk changes. Previously I was on develop snapshot from a few weeks back - and did not have this problem.\r\n\r\nNote:  `spack install netlib-scalapack` does not produce this error.\r\n",
